{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"futuresdirectives\">\n<span id=\"futuredirectives\"></span><h1>FuturesDirectives</h1>\n<p>Future directives can be used to run inner routes once the provided <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Future[T]</span></tt> has been completed.</p>\n<div class=\"toctree-wrapper compound\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"onComplete/\">onComplete</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"onSuccess/\">onSuccess</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"onFailure/\">onFailure</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>All future directives take a by-name parameter so that the parameter is not evaluated at route building time\nbut only when the request comes in.</p>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": false, "title": "FuturesDirectives", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-routing/future-directives/index", "next": {"link": "onComplete/", "title": "onComplete"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-routing/future-directives/onComplete", "onComplete", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-routing/form-field-directives/formFields", "formFields", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../", "title": "spray-routing"}, {"link": "../predefined-directives-by-trait/", "title": "Predefined Directives (by trait)"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">FuturesDirectives</a><ul>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../form-field-directives/formFields/", "title": "formFields"}, "metatags": ""}